sub_title: Operations and customer care expert; E-commerce, Ticketing and Online services; English teaching and translation
summary:
Enthusiastic and dynamic professional, with 10 years international experience within the E-commerce and online services industry. 
Native Portuguese, bilingual in English and Spanish, with excellent communication skills, great interpersonal skills and team management experience. 
A team player, with a flexible attitude and experience in the world of Teaching (presencial and online) E-commerce (Ticketing) and Customer Services. 

My teaching experience has been acquired through CELTA training and in the performance as a teacher at various language institutes, schools and private students in Portugal, England and Spain.

My E-commerce background comes from working at 4 different online Ticketing companies (Ticketmaster UK, Ticketbis, Last2Ticket and Ticketea by Eventbrite) where I performed in several areas from Customer Service, Account Management and Programming. 
I gained further experience with online services through my roles at Fever and, more recently, Cleanzy, where I held management level roles. 

Passionate about languages and communication, with a fond love for the English language in particular. 
Exceptional planning and organisational skills and great attention to detail and comfortable working in a fast paced, hands-on, growth orientated work environment.
